{"tid":397890,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"日本紋身","createTime":"2017-09-12T20:40:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T06:29:56.000Z","uid":90634,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a423d0b6e908710a8190d4ce38daf5aa7ea03d32","tid":397890,"uid":90634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T20:40:46.000Z","msg":"小弟下兩個星期會飛去大阪幾日<br />\n想話睇下會唔會有地方可以即日/約幾日內紋<br />\n都係紋簡單圖案 想留個念<br />\n之前都係係香港booking咁紋 未試過walkin<br />\n想問下有冇咁既地方 有既話有咩要注意"},{"pid":"052b96d8e8c6fd7ad6f4d085044434614fa6d46a","tid":397890,"uid":35370,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T20:47:11.000Z","msg":"知咩事啦"},{"pid":"2fda3014bae8d76264a5c24173b7596a20b9baf4","tid":397890,"uid":20658,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T22:23:37.000Z","msg":"唔係咁開心下話"},{"pid":"5751de059d78b92d91523ed209bdd759878be531","tid":397890,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T23:24:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://nextluxury.com/wp-content/uploads/awesome-leg-watermelon-with-bite-taken-out-tattoos-for-men.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextluxury.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fawesome-leg-watermelon-with-bite-taken-out-tattoos-for-men.jpg&h=58badece&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86ef48d6bc9611c57bef0ec540afe38aebe912a3","tid":397890,"uid":44267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T06:30:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係咁開心下話</blockquote><br />\n唔開心  唔開心"},{"pid":"00418db071606a431bfbd2b079296bad7082c9f8","tid":397890,"uid":5218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:47:14.000Z","msg":"戇撚鳩，可以 walk in 唔駛 book 好技術極有限。"},{"pid":"f3b54a0fe206162443b61964d025573292fee607","tid":397890,"uid":90634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:09:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戇撚鳩，可以 walk in 唔駛 book 好技術極有限。</blockquote><br />\n我打算紋好簡單既圖案"},{"pid":"03eea7deb67ff9a9bef0775f3dcbbe920c1edd18","